title: President Donald J. Trump Is Reducing The Cost Of Insulin And Improving Healthcare For Our Nation’s Seniors – The White House
content:
Fact Sheets			

		Healthcare	

Issued on:
May 26, 2020
No effort will be spared to give America’s seniors the care and support and devotion and love they have earned and that they deserve.
						President Donald J. Trump					LOWERING COST OF INSULIN FOR SENIORS: President Donald J. Trump and his Administration are lowering out-of-pocket insulin costs for Medicare’s seniors.
